{"title":"“Error:(1, 1) java:非法字符‘\\ufeff’”错误解决办法","date":"2020-03-06T15:13:18.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年3月6日","L":"2020/03/06","MM-DD":"03-06"},"author":"Clever Anastasia","thumbnail":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/10/GTzSSO.jpg","link":"2020/03/06/java03","comments":true,"tags":["Java","To be professional"],"categories":["Java"],"updated":"2020-05-10T14:29:21.282Z","content":"<h2><span id=\"出现原因\">出现原因</span></h2>\n<p>用Windows记事本打开并修改.java文件保存后重新编译运行项目出现“Error:(1, 1) java: 非法字符: ‘\\ufeff’”错误。<br>\n这是因为Windows记事本在修改UTF-8文件时会在文件开头添加BOM，导致IDEA不能正确读取.java文件从而报错。</p>\n<h2><span id=\"解决方法\">解决方法</span></h2>\n<p>在编辑器IDEA中将文件编码更改为UTF-16，再改回UTF-8即可，其实就相当于刷新了一下文件编码。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"属性attribute和property的区别","link":"2020/03/17/frontend01"},"next":{"title":"Java中floorMod方法的理解","link":"2020/02/28/java02"},"plink":"https://venanastasia.github.io/2020/03/06/java03/","toc":[{"id":null,"title":"出现原因","index":"1"},{"id":null,"title":"解决方法","index":"2"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Clever Anastasia","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International"}}